OL,3,CMan walks 30 miles up and down pier in
OL,4,Cmemory of his wife
OL,6,FA dedicated charity walker who
OL,7,Fsurvived open-heart surgery has walked
OL,8,F30-miles around a pier to mark three
OL,9,Fdecades of fundraising.
OL,11,FPaul Hobbs walked 111 laps around
OL,12,FWeston-super-Mare's Grand Pier on
OL,13,FThursday 15 August to mark the
OL,14,Fanniversary.
OL,16,FOver the past 30 years, the 75-year-
OL,17,Fold has raised more than a million
OL,18,Fpounds for various charities, saying
OL,19,Fthat fundraising is "part of his life".
