OL,3,CMan walks 30 miles up and down pier in
OL,4,Cmemory of his wife
OL,6,FHe said: "I only had major heart
OL,7,Fsurgery myself five years ago, so I do
OL,8,Fhave to be mindful, but I think it's
OL,9,Fabout you manage it - have a stop,
OL,10,Fpace yourself.
OL,12,F"After three decades, I still hope to
OL,13,Fkeep going for as long as I can, well
OL,14,Fas long as I am healthy and fit
OL,15,Fenough."
OL,17,F"I've had tremendous support, and I'd
OL,18,Flike to thank everbody over the past
OL,19,Fthirty years for helping me, help
OL,20,Fothers," he added.
